
CLEAR_SCREEN(2)           silmul_efun            CLEAR_SCREEN(2)

名稱
     clear_screen -  清除玩家螢幕

語法
     string clear_screen ();

描述
     If  this_player()  has  the  "vt100"  attribute  set,   this
     simul_efun  will  return  the  VT100  "screen  clear" escape
     sequence, so that the string will  clear  the  screen  on  a
     VT100-compatible terminal.  If "vt100" is not set, returns a
     null string.

     NOTE:  Do NOT use ed to edit the file vt100.c, or the escape
     sequences  will be corrupted.  (ed strips out escape charac-
     ters).

相關命令
     inverse,  blink,  bold,  underscore,  clear_line,   up_line,
     erase_line

作者
     Ichabod@TMI, 3/19/93
     wade@future 4/7/1996 翻譯

MudOS Release 0.9         Last change:                   3-19-93

